Patch Set 7:

eagle-36vm1: /tmp//mnt/lustre/f0.fsx_eagle-36vm1.fsxgood: No such file or directory
-- looks like that old fsx was ran;
some old fsx has the following code :

       strncat(goodfile, fname, 256);
        strcat (goodfile, ".fsxgood");
        fsxgoodfd = open(goodfile, O_RDWR|O_CREAT|O_TRUNC, 0666);
        if (fsxgoodfd < 0) {
                prterr(goodfile);
                exit(92);
        }
which creates /tmp//mnt/lustre/f0.fsx_eagle-36vm1.fsxgood instead of /tmp/f0.fsx_eagle-36vm1.fsxgood

New patchset sets FSX=$LUSTRE/tests/fsx by default
